# Qwen3.5-35B-A3B unsloth Dynamic Q4_K_XL (gurubot repack, thinking FORCED OFF, no vision)
# Goal: compare quant+version vs our qwen3.6-best (Ollama quant, 3.6). NOTE: this changes
# TWO variables at once (version 3.5 vs 3.6 AND quant unsloth-Q4_K_XL vs Ollama) - the result is conflated.
# Unsloth params identical to qwen36-best (temp 0.7, top_p 0.8, top_k 20, min_p 0, pp 1.5).
# Thinking is already disabled in the model (nothink repack), so --think=false is redundant but harmless.
# ollama create unsloth-q4xl-best -f configs/unsloth-q4xl.best.Modelfile
FROM gurubot/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-GGUF-unsloth-nothink:UD-Q4_K_XL
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER top_p 0.8
PARAMETER top_k 20
PARAMETER min_p 0
PARAMETER presence_penalty 1.5
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.0
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
PARAMETER num_predict 3000
